show.description: A maverick doctor walks into the hospital and turns the system on its head. As rules crumble and chaos brews, the question remains: will he change the world or be changed by it? Packed with gripping cases and emotional depth, this is one medical drama you can’t afford to miss. Watch "This Doctor is Very Powerful" Now!
